#### What goes where (extraction from current hardcoded values):

**.env** (tracked, shareable pattern — values are user-specific):
```bash
# ADO
ADO_ORG=https://dev.azure.com/{insert-ado-org-name}
ADO_PROJECT={insert-ado-project}
ADO_TEAM_ID={insert-ado-team-id}
ADO_AREA_PATH={insert-ado-area-path}
ADO_ITERATION={insert-ado-iteration}
ADO_API_VERSION=7.1

# GitLab
GITLAB_HOST={insert-gitlab-host}

# Paths
REPOS_ROOT={insert-repos-root}
GEOBRAIN_VAULT={insert-geobrain-vault-path}
DEV_VAULT={insert-dev-vault-path}
LLM_OUTPUT=~/llm/output

# KSM
KSM_BINARY=~/.local/bin/ksm
KSM_INI=~/.keeper/keeper.ini
```

**.secrets** (GITIGNORED — never printed, never loaded into LLM context):
```bash
# Keeper UIDs for secret retrieval (not the secrets themselves)
ADO_PAT_KEEPER_UID={insert-keeper-uid}
ADO_PAT_KEEPER_TITLE={insert-ado-pat-keeper-title}
GITLAB_PAT_KEEPER_TITLE={insert-gitlab-pat-keeper-title}
```

**profile.md** (tracked — identity and preferences):
