### Scripts Path Updates

All scripts currently hardcode `~/copilot/{insert-team-tag}/` paths. They need to:
1. Source `~/llm/env/.env` for config values
2. Write output to `$LLM_OUTPUT/` instead of `~/copilot/{insert-team-tag}/`
3. Read profile from `~/llm/env/profile.md` instead of `~/copilot/{insert-team-tag}/geobrain-profile.md`

| Script | Hardcoded Paths to Update |
|---|---|
| `sprint-sync.py` | `PROFILE_PATH`, `OUTPUT_PATH` |
| `team-index-sync.py` | `PROFILE_PATH`, `GEOBRAIN_VAULT` output path |
| `project-status.py` | `PROFILE_PATH`, vault paths |
